	tristate "HackRF"
	depends on VIDEO_V4L2
	select VIDEOBUF2_VMALLOC
	---help---
	  This is a video4linux2 driver for HackRF SDR device.

	  To compile this driver as a module, choose M here: the
	  module will be called hackrf

